<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/608254-does-this-book-touch-on-the-topic-of">Does this book touch on the topic of beluga whales at all? Or can someone recommend a good non fiction read that discusses beluga whales in captivity and the wild?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_608254'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F23014804-beneath-the-surface">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/608254-does-this-book-touch-on-the-topic-of">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/608254-does-this-book-touch-on-the-topic-of">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/3049657-victoria"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1264608339i/3049657._UY100_CR18,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3049657-victoria">Victoria</a>
