        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1484731305" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16339639604225748937">Finished it in one sitting. Never gave much thought to what it takes to train killer whales. It was such an eye opening. Great learning experience. RIP to all those who lost their lives working with those amazing and unpredictable animals. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


